'''Al Jazeera Sports Club''' ({{lang-ar|نادي الجزيرة الرياضي}}), is an [[Egypt]]ian sports club based in [[Mersa Matruh]], Egypt. The club is mainly known for its [[Association football|football]] team, which currently plays in the [[Egyptian Second Division]], the second-highest league in the [[Egyptian football league system]].<ref name="Soccerway">{{cite web |last1=Soccerway |title=Al Jazeera SC on Soccerway |url=https://us.soccerway.com/teams/united-arab-emirates/al-jazeera-abu-dhabi/5488/ |accessdate=20 August 2018}}</ref>

