{{Infobox football biography | name = Lulu Statia | fullname = Luivienna Statia | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1997|4|25|df=yes}} | image = | birth_place = | height = 1.78 m | position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]] | currentclub = [[FC Dordrecht]] | clubnumber = 16 | youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = RKSV RCD | youthyears2 = | youthclubs2 = EBOH | youthyears3 = | youthclubs3 = [[SC Feyenoord]] | youthyears4 = 2008–2016 | youthclubs4 = [[FC Dordrecht]] | years1 = 2016– | clubs1 = [[FC Dordrecht]] | caps1 = 10 | goals1 = 0 | pcupdate = 27 May 2017 | ntupdate = }}
'''Luivienna "Lulu" Statia''' (born 25 April 1997) is a [[Curaçao]]an [[association football|football]] player who plays for [[FC Dordrecht]]. He also holds [[Netherlands|Dutch]] citizenship.
==Club career== He made his professional debut in the [[Eerste Divisie]] for [[FC Dordrecht]] on 25 November 2016 in a game against [[FC Eindhoven]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Soccerway|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2016/11/25/netherlands/eerste-divisie/fc-eindhoven/bvo-fc-dordrecht/2240698/|title=Game Report by Soccerway|date=25 November 2016}}</ref>
