{{infobox country at games | games = World Aquatics Championships | NF = FSM | NFname = Federated States of Micronesia Swimming Association | year = 2013 | flagcaption = [[Flag of Federated States of Micronesia]] | oldcode= | website = | location = [[Barcelona]], [[Spain]] | competitors = '''2''' | sports = '''1''' | officials= | gold=0 | silver=0 | bronze=0 | rank= | appearances = auto | app_begin_year=2001 | seealso = }}
The '''[[Federated States of Micronesia]]''' competed at the [[2013 World Aquatics Championships]] in [[Barcelona]], [[Spain]] between 19 July and 4 August 2013.
